Package structure

Class HttpRequest

java.lang.Object
structure.Request
structure.HttpRequest
public final class HttpRequest
extends Request
Send http request in different http request method with custom param and get return json data.

This class is extending from Request class.

This class should be working along with HttpBody, since the getters and setters of requestBody, requestCookie, responseBody, responseCookie are accept/return HttpBody type object.

Since:
1.0
Version:
2.1
Author:
Cloudy Young
